00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
You don't need to ask.

480
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Gulrez will be on your team.

481
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Announce the names.

482
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Maheen Aurangzeb,

483
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Gulrez Akhtar,

484
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Neelam Wali Ahmed, and... And...

485
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Kaneez Maruf Ahmed.

486
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Imagine you're playing against the British Empire.

487
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
But I'm not as great a cricketer as he's making it sound like.

488
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Toss the coin.

489
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Gulrez will toss the coin for me.

490
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
May I go from our side?

491
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
No.

492
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
I got this one.

